Thanks to Szabolcs Szakacsits, pavuk have now its own mailing list. It
is used for discussions about pavuk development and usage, you can post
there your questions, suggestions or bug reports.

Official language for this list is english, but I personaly accept also
slovak or czech languages.

This mailing list is hosted at YahooGroups site for free. To subscribe,
send empty message to <pavuk-subscribe@yahoogroups.com> or you can fill
subscription form at pavuk homepage.

YahooGroups also provides archiving of mailing list trafic, so you can
access it at http://groups.yahoo.com/group/pavuk/.

